  "title": "Fix cross-feature-root file-scope conflict false positive",
  "agent_type": "planner",
  "description": "The scheduler's _beads_conflict() method incorrectly blocks beads in different feature roots from running concurrently when their expected_files/expected_globs overlap. Because different feature roots use different Git worktrees, there is no real runtime collision \u2014 the conflict is a false positive. This epic applies a one-line fix to gate _scopes_overlap() on same_feature_tree, and adds a regression test to prevent recurrence.",
